des:
Ask for Physics Facts, and learn about interesting facts about physics.

Physics Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Random Physics Facts".

At any time, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
